   DTD for Event-B unchecked context files.

   This DTD concerns context files that have been directly entered by
   the user or generated by a front-end plug-in such as U2B.

   IMPORTANT NOTE: All "contents" attribute will disappear in the next
   version of the tools (expected mid-November 2006).

